{"tid":2263669,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"15歲少年疑示威現場掟水樽 彭亮廷裁定罪成 還押壁屋候判","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:11:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T13:32:42.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":38,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2b550bd38d5dcdcea80100b3a42c9df6f668cd79","tid":2263669,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:11:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10817\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10817&d=L3LYojiCq%2FWCCnzMgLa5KD9kuezr8BQg8uGmIe3q97E%3D&h=f29b3c1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10817</a><br />\n<br />\n#西九龍裁判法院第廿一庭 （少年庭）<br />\n#彭亮廷裁判官<br />\n#庭外消息<br />\n<br />\n👤*(15) #裁決 (#1102旺角 在公眾地方作出擾亂秩序的行為）<br />\n<br />\n裁定：<br />\n被告確曾投擲水樽向警察防線，並懷有意圖激使他人破壞社會安寧。控方無合理疑點舉證<br />\n<br />\n🛑裁定控罪確立🛑<br />\n<br />\n裁判官索取：感化官報告，社會服務令報告，更生報告，勞教中心報告，青少年罪犯評估專責小組報告<br />\n青少年評估報告需時3星期<br />\n<br />\n押後至11月20日上午930 沙田裁判法院第三庭宣判<br />\n<br />\n🔴期間還押壁屋🔴"},{"pid":"2af1021af3689c81d2eab5e5446521349612fe5a","tid":2263669,"uid":323740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"+1"},{"pid":"1e5cceedc00c0c918d0dcca08a57e9a16e548c27","tid":2263669,"uid":216163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:15:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84ecb171c66d5562eda7079e76622569e326806a","tid":2263669,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:18:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7346b6b392190c98625fc8675cb